             was indicted for that <rs id="t18140706-97-off539" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t18140706-97-off539" type="offenceCategory" value="theft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18140706-97-off539" type="offenceSubcategory" value="embezzlement"></interp>
               he, on the <rs id="t18140706-97-cd540" type="crimeDate">28th of May</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18140706-97-off539 t18140706-97-cd540"></join>, was <rs id="t18140706-97-deflabel541" type="occupation">servant</rs>
                     <join result="persNameOccupation" targOrder="Y" targets="t18140706-97-defend808 t18140706-97-deflabel541"></join> to 
                     
                        <persName id="t18140706-97-victim810" type="victimName">
                           William 
                           Hewitson
